For Users:

    Component:      OpenID::self
    Instance:       ::

    Comment Access: User is able to view and manage all aspects of his OpenIDs
                    associated with his account, including associating new OpenIDs,
                    removing OpenIDs, changing the primary OpenID, etc.

    No other access levels are used with respect to users.

For Admins:

    Component:      OpenID::settings
    Instance:       ::

    Admin Access:   User is able to modify the module settings for the OpenID module.

    Component:      Users::
    Instance:       ::

    Delete Access:  User is able to delete OpenIDs associated with a user account, but
                    only when deleting that user account through the Users module.
